en_205994_0	Troops of the 9 Vijayabahu Infantry Regiment (VIR) of the 571 Brigade organized a Shramadana campaign on Saturday (6) to clean the Durgai Amman Kovil and its premises in Barathipuram under the guidance of Brigadier A.S Hewawitharana, General Officer Commanding, 57 Division and under the supervision of the 571 Brigade Commander.
en_205994_1	The campaign was organized with the intention of further strengthening of bonds of goodwill of devotees and assist Kovil trustees and civilians.
en_205994_2	One officer and 15 soldiers attended the cleaning campaign with some civilians.
